\pard\plain \fi720\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Given our guiding principal, we need to figure out what our mechanics are.  We have a scene I really like. What does this scene imply about the rest of the game?}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 1. Memories have power/Bonds have power}
