\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 4. What are some tricks we can play regarding memories}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab * Amnesia Loop - the player has done this before}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab * Amnesiac Dissonance - multiple characters remember a past/alternate reality in which things may have been different for some of them}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab * We can make the whole thing a Memory Gambit. This would be fun to make!}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
